{"tid":1956753,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！DI撚全部同我入嚟！Ive仔的曙光","createTime":"2020-04-03T11:38:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T18:37:57.000Z","uid":273794,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"200a0fb7e4f9465ec30771c52a0fed4311d806cb","tid":1956753,"uid":273794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T11:38:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Ad8xdG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Ad8xdG.jpg&h=6464f531&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cLZPgFv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcLZPgFv.png&h=a5d6acbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信大家都收到學費單<br />\n即使市道再差，網上學習再冇用都好<br />\n但學校係呢種情況下依然要求學生交全額學費<br />\n無疑係逼學生交錢攞學位<br />\n大部分學生都認為根本學習唔到課程內容。<br />\n<br />\n不過唔緊要！飛雲！<br />\n依家HKDI嘅學生會決定<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>聯署罷交學費</strong></span><br />\n而且要求實名認證，令成件事更有群眾嘅效應<br />\n大家只需要入去填左去，影埋自己張學生證<br />\n鍾意就講低埋唔交學費嘅原因<br />\n依家聯署目標係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2000人</span></strong></span><br />\n因為大家都知道，除非罷交嘅人數夠多先會令到學校痛<br />\n<br />\n以下credit 一段：<br />\n由上年十月要求學校交出CCTV一事開始直至現時疫情事件一直停課。而且直到一月才有online class，所以十月到十二月是完全沒有任何課堂，亦沒有享用學校資源。<br />\n<br />\n因為我地學校比較特殊，已經兩個sem都冇上過堂咁滯<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我地上個學期可以忍，今期唔可以再忍！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">聯署表格：</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><a href=\"https://forms.gle/m7NaTzaYBgGxXeMd8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2Fm7NaTzaYBgGxXeMd8&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2Bosqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=5331d741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/m7NaTzaYBgGxXeMd8</a></span></span><br />\n依家機會嚟左，希望大家可以幫手出分力<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">幫手推 幫手填 幫手Share</span></strong></span><br />\n行多一步先會令件事有可能成功。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（學費調整聯署行動Channel）</span></span></strong><br />\nTelegram：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/HtXLZRtK4yuAwgRGC2guBA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FHtXLZRtK4yuAwgRGC2guBA&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2Bosqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=86be7b2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/HtXLZRtK4yuAwgRGC2guBA</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">學生會IG</span></strong></span> (有問題或者意見可以搵佢地提出）<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/vouves.dilwl?igshid=10dn0y7olwv3l\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fvouves.dilwl%3Figshid%3D10dn0y7olwv3l&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2Bosqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=0540dde3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/vouves.dilwl?igshid=10dn0y7olwv3l</a><br />\n<br />\n最後，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">求幫推！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"bec5f373f958bf605233384ce60827da49f4cba9","tid":1956753,"uid":25516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"200a0fb7e4f9465ec30771c52a0fed4311d806cb","tid":1956753,"uid":273794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T11:38:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Ad8xdG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Ad8xdG.jpg&h=6464f531&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cLZPgFv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcLZPgFv.png&h=a5d6acbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信大家都收到學費單<br />\n即使市道再差，網上學習再冇用都好<br />\n但學校係呢種情況下依然要求學生交全額學費<br />\n無疑係逼學生交錢攞學位<br />\n大部分學生都認為根本學習唔到課程內容。<br />\n<br />\n不過唔緊要！飛雲！<br />\n依家HKDI嘅學生會決定<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>聯署罷交學費</strong></span><br />\n而且要求實名認證，令成件事更有群眾嘅效應<br />\n大家只需要入去填左去，影埋自己張學生證<br />\n鍾意就講低埋唔交學費嘅原因<br />\n依家聯署目標